These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, house, pop
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, thai, turkish
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, romance, drama
1. the person watching drama movies is in an even position##4
2. the thai is on the left of the indian##1
3. the fan of classical is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the thai is in an even position##4
5. the fan of pop is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | classical     | house    |
| Nationality   | turkish   | thai          | indian   |
| Movie-Genre         | documentary | drama | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, cabbage, nectarine
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, cain, dannemann
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, musician, teacher
1. the teacher is the person eating nectarine##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the teacher##3
3. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
4. the musician is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
5. the teacher is in an even position##4
6. the teacher is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food    | avocado     | nectarine  | cabbage  |
| Cigar   | dannemann | cain | aristoff    |
| Job     | dancer      | teacher    | musician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, kiwi, plum
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, reggae
City: marseilles, berlin, rome
1. the person traveling to marseilles is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to rome is the person eating apple##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating apple##1
5. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Food          | apple         | plum     | kiwi   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | funk     | reggae |
| City         | rome | marseilles | berlin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, mirinda
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, papaya, cranberry
3 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, snake
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Beverage   | coffee | mirinda  | hot-chocolate |
| Food        | cranberry | papaya  | pomegranate |
| Pet        | ferret | goldfish | snake         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
House: farmhouse, townhouse, cottage
There are 3 different nationalities: american, australian, chinese
3 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, mouse
1. the american is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
2. the australian is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
4. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
5. the cottage house is on the far left##1
6. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| House   | cottage | farmhouse  | townhouse  |
| Nationality   | australian  | american | chinese |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | mouse    | bird    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, sprite
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, chess, singing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, animation, drama
1. the person drinking cola is between the person watching drama movies and the person who's hobby is singing##2
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person watching animation movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Beverage    | sprite  | cola  | milk        |
| Hobby       | singing | chess | board-games |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | animation   | drama   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, sports, western
3 different pets are kept: frog, goldfish, rat
3 different games are played: whist, backgammon, billiard
1. the person watching sports movies is between the owner of the frog and the person watching western movies##2
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | sports        | western |
| Pet           | frog   | goldfish      | rat     |
| Game         | billiard | backgammon | whist    |

