.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, nurse, photographer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, ambient, reggae
There are 3 different nationalities: german, russian, thai
1. the nurse is on the far right##1
2. the fan of ambient is the fan of ambient##1
3. the german is on the left or right of the thai##3
4. the chef is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
5. the thai is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
6. the fan of reggae is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Job           | photographer | chef        | nurse   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | reggae | classical    |
| Nationality   | thai         | german      | russian |

