4. the pilot is on the left of the dancer##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2      |    3    |
| Job         | videographer | pilot      | dancer  |
| Pet         | bird         | snake      | pony    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea         | juice | mirinda |

