.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-15::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bus, motorbike
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, r&b, trance
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, pony
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the fan of punk is the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the person driving the bus is the fan of r&b##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |   3    |
| Transport   | bus      | motorbike | airplane |
| Music-Genre   | r&b        | punk         | trance |
| Pet           | chinchilla | pony         | frog   |

