1. the owner of the hedgehog is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the musician##1
5. the electrician is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Hobby         | cooking   | camping     | hiking   |
| Job           | mechanic  | electrician | musician |
| Pet   | hedgehog | dog     | snake |

